==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Richesse
<hw>Rich"esse</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Riches</er>.]</ety> <def>Wealth; riches. See the Note under
<er>Riches</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some man desireth for to have <qex>richesse</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>richesse</qex> of all heavenly grace.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Richly</ent>⟦br⟧
